<recipe>
<title>
Slow Cooker Overnight Pecan Pie Oatmeal Recipe
</title>
<details>
AUTHOR: i heart eating
PREP TIME: 5 minutes
COOK TIME: 6 hours
TOTAL TIME: 6 hours 5 minutes
COURSE: Breakfast
CUISINE: American
KEYWORD: crock pot, oatmeal, slow cooker
SERVINGS: 6
</details>
<ingredients><ingredient amount="12.0">Milk</ingredient></ingredients>
<instructions>
Grease slow cooker.
In a large bowl, stir together oats, water, milk, brown sugar, and maple flavor.
Pour into slow cooker (I used a 2 quart).
Cover, and cook on low for 6-8 hours.
To serve, top with additional brown sugar, real maple syrup, and chopped pecans.
</instructions>
<cuisine>American</cuisine></recipe>